{"tid":847353,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘TOP5著名律師行招手 傳朱千雪將轉行投身法律界","createTime":"2018-10-04T06:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T01:41:26.000Z","uid":9573,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cc7bd667b8c5fe272a7663b2d5d5f6c24995c228","tid":847353,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"2年港姐季軍朱千雪（Tracy），入行後一直獲無綫力捧，更憑首次擔正女一嘅劇集《EU超時任務》人氣急升，繼而成功入屋。之後，佢選擇向無綫請假重返校園增值自己，先後修讀企業傳播管理系碩士及法律系博士課程。唔少網民都諗住佢完成學業之後，可以多啲喺幕前見到佢，點知千雪已經計劃轉行，投身法律界。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HWupvVs6v1bLiUu8hdTmZQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--/https://66.media.tumblr.com/86441102aabd22cb18f40a09f3b9878e/tumblr_inline_pg0amhKPgn1u03abq_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHWupvVs6v1bLiUu8hdTmZQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F86441102aabd22cb18f40a09f3b9878e%2Ftumblr_inline_pg0amhKPgn1u03abq_1280.jpg&h=6b82c0fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n千雪有樣、有學歷又有家底，博士課程未正式畢業，已經去律師行做實習，有指最近仲有一間位於金鐘嘅top 5著名律師行向佢招手，為佢預留職位，真係前途無可限量呀！今日就有報道指千雪唔再留戀娛樂圈，將會正式轉行做「Law界女神」，佢仲話自己一直好想讀法律，因為加拿大唔可以直接讀法律，要讀咗學士課程先，所以佢讀完書就返咗香港，之前又工作又讀碩士，而家啱晒timing。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CNM28JenD0tUipgpu6BsYQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--/https://66.media.tumblr.com/057e5a9bd20e83915551f3423e91aca5/tumblr_inline_pg0an9JHP11u03abq_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCNM28JenD0tUipgpu6BsYQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F057e5a9bd20e83915551f3423e91aca5%2Ftumblr_inline_pg0an9JHP11u03abq_1280.jpg&h=035a70e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然千雪同無綫仲有合約，不過佢已經開始減少拍劇，主要都係演出綜藝節目及出席商場活動。法律知識豐富嘅佢，雖然冇參演劇集《白色強人》，不過佢都有為劇集提供法律方面嘅知識。之前有傳媒問佢會唔會退出娛圈，佢就話到時先算，仲話到佢約滿嘅時候，可能係公司唔簽佢呢！<br />\n睇嚟佢已經轉行心切，鍾意千雪嘅朋友就祝福佢啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TKx0MhyLuF1ZnlFq2RZkIg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--/https://66.media.tumblr.com/3f99b66558f1acd68638ff15b628d77b/tumblr_inline_pg0amyxos51u03abq_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTKx0MhyLuF1ZnlFq2RZkIg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F3f99b66558f1acd68638ff15b628d77b%2Ftumblr_inline_pg0amyxos51u03abq_1280.jpg&h=ec25ccda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cosmopolitan.com.hk/var/cosmopolitanhk/storage/images/entertainment/tracy-chu-become-lawyer/node_258572/2604449-1-chi-HK/_1_img_750_h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fcosmopolitanhk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fentertainment%2Ftracy-chu-become-lawyer%2Fnode_258572%2F2604449-1-chi-HK%2F_1_img_750_h.jpg&h=22d014b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBNTqGs.img?h=450&amp;w=799&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=1039&amp;y=274\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBNTqGs.img%3Fh%3D450%26w%3D799%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D1039%26y%3D274&h=d53e403c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cosmopolitan.com.hk/var/cosmopolitanhk/storage/images/entertainment/tracy-chu-become-lawyer/node_258563/2604368-1-chi-HK/_1_img_750_h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fcosmopolitanhk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fentertainment%2Ftracy-chu-become-lawyer%2Fnode_258563%2F2604368-1-chi-HK%2F_1_img_750_h.jpg&h=78ebc2c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/859827/org/4f65ee7c99768c598f04c53553224eaf.jpg/rNRowqn3hlFDVJyY0yuSzahCJGtC7-joxKC1dc